  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rohingya Crisis (Scottish Govt) Emergency Shelter &amp; WASH, Jamtoli Camp (CCDB)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. 1080 Shelters Kits will be distributed to new arrivals prioritizing the most vulnerable groups (containing 18ft/12ft tarpaulin, plastic ground sheet and 30m rope) . Part of the shelter support will be land identification for vulnerable families as families with capacity to buy and build are establishing new sites on their own. 
2. 1080 Water, Sanitation and Hygiene Kits will be distributed. Each kit will contain one 20 litre bucket, 2 mugs, 4 bathing soap bars, 5 laundry soap bars, 500 ml disinfection liquid savlon/detol 500 ml, 2 metre menstrual cloth / 4 pieces, 1 soap case and 10 oral rehydration salt / Orsalins.</narrative>
  </description>
